            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I studied here for 10 years. Worst school in Jaipur. 1) no tight security 2) no ac in classrooms 3) no proper handwashes or mirrors in washrooms 4) lots of homework given which often gets stressful for children 5) teachers always scold you and complain to your parents for absurd reasons for eg not completing your hw 6) teachers and the staff are very mean and they humiliate you in front of the class 7) students are always bunking, bullying, abusing, etc 8) toxic environment 9) parking facility is a joke 10) the fees is too high, it is just a money making school. They do not care about students at all. I don't recommend this school to anyone.",
          "publisher": {
